# cometdata

<!-- badges: start -->
<!-- badges: end -->

This is simply a repository to hold data for COMET, mainly the `gen_and_spawn` module. You will also need for this for `run_simulation`. For more information see [https://github.com/ClevelandClinicQHS/COMET#readme](https://github.com/ClevelandClinicQHS/COMET#readme)
